473
00:30:44,440 --> 00:30:45,859
[SPEAKER_00] Imaj križ tetoviranu srcu

474
00:30:45,859 --> 00:30:47,839
[SPEAKER_00] koji ti niko ne može oduzeti.

475
00:30:47,839 --> 00:30:49,380
[SPEAKER_00] Cijeli tvoj život govori

476
00:30:49,380 --> 00:30:51,240
[SPEAKER_00] o Isusu Hristu živome Bogu.

477
00:30:51,240 --> 00:30:54,059
[SPEAKER_00] Nije nužna ta tetovaža ovoga simbola.

478
00:30:54,059 --> 00:30:55,759
[SPEAKER_00] Ali razumijem, ako neko to želi,

479
00:30:55,759 --> 00:30:57,339
[SPEAKER_00] samo nek onda pripazi

480
00:30:57,339 --> 00:31:00,480
[SPEAKER_00] da to bude sve što je više moguće sigurno.

481
00:31:01,420 --> 00:31:03,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ali neki rizik određeni ipak postoji,

482
00:31:03,240 --> 00:31:04,700
[SPEAKER_00] ja mislim, kod sve tetovaže.

483
00:31:04,700 --> 00:31:06,579
[SPEAKER_00] Nije baš to za kožu najbolje.

484
00:31:06,579 --> 00:31:09,619
[SPEAKER_00] I onda rak kože čak, mislim, može...

485
00:31:09,619 --> 00:31:11,740
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je na suncu tetovaža, isto je ono drugačije.

486
00:31:11,740 --> 00:31:13,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ima neke rizike,

487
00:31:13,559 --> 00:31:14,859
[SPEAKER_00] zrastvene, zato bolje ne.

488
00:31:15,339 --> 00:31:18,140
[SPEAKER_00] Ali opet, ovaj nije to sad nužno grijeh.

489
00:31:18,140 --> 00:31:21,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ali problem je kad se stavi nešto

490
00:31:21,180 --> 00:31:21,779
[SPEAKER_00] što ima

491
00:31:21,779 --> 00:31:25,299
[SPEAKER_00] totalno opasno i pogrešno značenje.

492
00:31:25,299 --> 00:31:26,559
[SPEAKER_00] Kao te to važu?

493
00:31:26,559 --> 00:31:27,519
[SPEAKER_00] A to ga isto ima, jel?

494
00:31:27,519 --> 00:31:28,059
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

495
00:31:28,720 --> 00:31:29,980
[SPEAKER_00] To je onda bolje skinuti skroz.

496
00:31:29,980 --> 00:31:31,039
[SPEAKER_00] Tako te to važu.

497
00:31:31,039 --> 00:31:32,299
[SPEAKER_00] Jasno, da.

498
00:31:32,299 --> 00:31:34,779
[SPEAKER_01] Pazi, sljedeće pitanje.

499
00:31:34,779 --> 00:31:38,819
[SPEAKER_01] Je li loše ako ne podržavamo molitelje na trgu?

500
00:31:38,819 --> 00:31:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Misli ste na molitvu muške krunice, očito.

501
00:31:41,000 --> 00:31:42,819
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

502
00:31:42,819 --> 00:31:46,339
[SPEAKER_00] To ste na njih misli.

503
00:31:46,339 --> 00:31:48,539
[SPEAKER_00] Prije svega, mislim da treba,

504
00:31:48,539 --> 00:31:51,359
[SPEAKER_00] kome je stalo, kog to zanima,

505
00:31:51,359 --> 00:31:54,059
[SPEAKER_00] nek potraži što su oni rekli sami o sebi.

506
00:31:54,059 --> 00:31:57,940
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto oni to mole u istinu i tako dalje.

507
00:31:58,019 --> 00:31:59,299
[SPEAKER_00] nešta, drugi govore o njima.

508
00:31:59,299 --> 00:32:01,759
[SPEAKER_00] Mi stvaramo sudove o nekome

509
00:32:01,759 --> 00:32:04,720
[SPEAKER_00] i nečemu na temelju toga što nam drugi govore

510
00:32:04,720 --> 00:32:06,700
[SPEAKER_00] i onda povjerujemo ono što nam drugi kažu,

511
00:32:06,700 --> 00:32:09,019
[SPEAKER_00] a bez da smo sami nešto ispitali

512
00:32:09,019 --> 00:32:10,319
[SPEAKER_00] i upoznali i tako dalje.

513
00:32:10,319 --> 00:32:12,920
[SPEAKER_00] Na kraju krajeva,

514
00:32:12,920 --> 00:32:15,599
[SPEAKER_00] u našem društvu trebao bi svako imati

515
00:32:15,599 --> 00:32:17,019
[SPEAKER_00] slobodu nekog izričaja

516
00:32:17,019 --> 00:32:18,559
[SPEAKER_00] i to je isto čudno.

517
00:32:18,559 --> 00:32:21,759
[SPEAKER_00] Kad se izruguju kršćanske vrijednosti

518
00:32:21,759 --> 00:32:25,460
[SPEAKER_00] pod hrinkom umjetnosti,

519
00:32:25,460 --> 00:32:27,500
[SPEAKER_00] umjetničke sloboda, znači baš se vrijeđa,

520
00:32:27,559 --> 00:32:29,599
[SPEAKER_00] ponižava, izruguje, nikom ništa.

521
00:32:29,599 --> 00:32:30,559
[SPEAKER_00] To je sve sloboda.

522
00:32:30,559 --> 00:32:33,940
[SPEAKER_00] Sloboda izričaja, sloboda ovoga, sloboda onoga.

523
00:32:33,940 --> 00:32:35,460
[SPEAKER_00] A kada kršćani tako mole

524
00:32:35,460 --> 00:32:38,339
[SPEAKER_00] na trgu, to smeta.

525
00:32:38,339 --> 00:32:41,539
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, jedna sloboda ne smeta nikome,

526
00:32:41,539 --> 00:32:43,519
[SPEAKER_00] nema nekakvu osudu,

527
00:32:43,519 --> 00:32:45,640
[SPEAKER_00] a druga sloboda smeta.

528
00:32:45,640 --> 00:32:47,240
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, prečudno.

529
00:32:48,839 --> 00:32:51,619
[SPEAKER_00] To su se baš oglasili protestantske ove zajednice

530
00:32:51,619 --> 00:32:55,660
[SPEAKER_00] u znak podrške njima, jer nije u redu da trpe tamo nasilja,

531
00:32:55,660 --> 00:32:57,220
[SPEAKER_00] da ih neko napadne dok se oni mole.

532
00:32:57,220 --> 00:32:58,980
[SPEAKER_00] Da, protestanti koji ne mole krunicu, mislim,

533
00:32:58,980 --> 00:33:01,920
[SPEAKER_01] nemaju neki interes, kako bi rekao.

534
00:33:01,920 --> 00:33:02,859
[SPEAKER_00] Kako genijalno.

535
00:33:02,859 --> 00:33:04,839
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, protestanti koji ne mole krunicu,

536
00:33:04,839 --> 00:33:06,740
[SPEAKER_00] išli su se oglasiti.

537
00:33:06,740 --> 00:33:07,720
[SPEAKER_00] Svaka im čast, jel?

538
00:33:08,519 --> 00:33:13,779
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, mi ne moramo podržavati sa takav način molitve.

539
00:33:13,779 --> 00:33:16,220
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mora to biti svačiji način.

540
00:33:16,220 --> 00:33:18,900
[SPEAKER_00] To je ljepota crkve, da je crkva raznolika široka.

541
00:33:18,900 --> 00:33:21,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ima puno pokreta u crkvi.

542
00:33:21,240 --> 00:33:23,559
[SPEAKER_00] Od karizmanskog pokreta do, ne znam,

543
00:33:23,559 --> 00:33:25,099
[SPEAKER_00] neokatekumenskog pokreta,

544
00:33:25,099 --> 00:33:27,079
[SPEAKER_00] toliki redovničkih zajednica.

545
00:33:27,079 --> 00:33:29,119
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, stotine karizmi.

546
00:33:29,119 --> 00:33:31,460
[SPEAKER_00] I svaka je plo duha svetoga.

547
00:33:31,460 --> 00:33:33,500
[SPEAKER_00] I ako nešto nije moj način,

548
00:33:33,500 --> 00:33:35,119
[SPEAKER_00] pa neću ja pljuvati to.

549
00:33:35,119 --> 00:33:37,500
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ja sam dominikanac, pa ću pljuvati po

550
00:33:37,500 --> 00:33:39,480
[SPEAKER_00] nekima koji su

551
00:33:39,480 --> 00:33:41,500
[SPEAKER_00] Franjevci, neokatekumeni, Isusovci.

552
00:33:41,500 --> 00:33:43,279
[SPEAKER_00] Nekad sada našalim na račun Franjevaca.

553
00:33:43,279 --> 00:33:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] To su naše interne šale,

554
00:33:46,380 --> 00:33:47,599
[SPEAKER_00] ali to nije zla volja.

555
00:33:47,599 --> 00:33:49,880
[SPEAKER_00] Crkva ima širinu.

556
00:33:49,880 --> 00:33:52,220
[SPEAKER_00] Karizmi, poslanja, zajednica,

557
00:33:52,220 --> 00:33:54,380
[SPEAKER_00] svega i sve to, plo duha svetoga.

558
00:33:54,380 --> 00:33:55,660
[SPEAKER_00] Ako nešto nije moj način,

559
00:33:55,660 --> 00:33:58,259
[SPEAKER_00] ne znači da nije dobar način

560
00:33:58,259 --> 00:33:59,599
[SPEAKER_00] za neku drugu osobu, jel?

561
00:33:59,599 --> 00:34:02,200
[SPEAKER_00] Niko sam ja da pljujem onda po svima

562
00:34:02,200 --> 00:34:04,460
[SPEAKER_00] koji su drugačiji, a u katoličkoj su crkvi, jel?

563
00:34:04,460 --> 00:34:06,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo su vjernici, lajici,

564
00:34:06,640 --> 00:34:08,340
[SPEAKER_00] koji su se organizirali,

565
00:34:08,340 --> 00:34:09,559
[SPEAKER_00] koje je jedno civilno odruženje,

566
00:34:09,559 --> 00:34:11,360
[SPEAKER_00] imaju pravo na to legitimno u državi.

567
00:34:11,360 --> 00:34:13,760
[SPEAKER_00] To je to. To nije inicijativa crkve,

568
00:34:13,760 --> 00:34:16,079
[SPEAKER_00] zato crkva tu se ne oglašava previše,

569
00:34:16,079 --> 00:34:18,619
[SPEAKER_00] jer nije to došao poticaj

570
00:34:18,619 --> 00:34:20,599
[SPEAKER_00] s nekog vrha

571
00:34:20,599 --> 00:34:21,960
[SPEAKER_00] crkvene hirarhije, nego

572
00:34:21,960 --> 00:34:24,460
[SPEAKER_00] odolazi od baze, od samih vjernika.

573
00:34:24,460 --> 00:34:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oni misle da je to potrebno,

574
00:34:26,000 --> 00:34:28,199
[SPEAKER_00] njihova savjest je čista, to je najbitnije,

575
00:34:28,199 --> 00:34:30,940
[SPEAKER_00] znaju što žele i zašto to rade.

576
00:34:31,400 --> 00:34:33,219
[SPEAKER_00] Imaju i svećenike koji ih poznaju,

577
00:34:33,219 --> 00:34:35,980
[SPEAKER_00] ko duhovnici ih prate i daju im savjete,

578
00:34:35,980 --> 00:34:37,860
[SPEAKER_00] neki možda ne daju uvijek najbolje savjete,

579
00:34:37,860 --> 00:34:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] ko zna što,

580
00:34:38,420 --> 00:34:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] kako je to sve ne poznam, ono toliko duboko,

581
00:34:42,000 --> 00:34:44,960
[SPEAKER_00] ali znam da neke svećenike oni poznaju,

582
00:34:44,960 --> 00:34:46,619
[SPEAKER_00] da im oni pomažu i tako dalje.

583
00:34:46,679 --> 00:34:48,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ih isto više podržavam nego ne.

584
00:34:48,579 --> 00:34:50,579
[SPEAKER_00] Podržavam, u principu i podržavam.

585
00:34:50,579 --> 00:34:54,139
[SPEAKER_00] Jer znam neke od njih osobno

586
00:34:54,139 --> 00:34:55,519
[SPEAKER_00] i znam da je njihova savjest čista,

587
00:34:55,519 --> 00:34:56,320
[SPEAKER_00] nakana, dobra.

588
00:34:56,320 --> 00:34:58,840
[SPEAKER_00] A sad način na koji to ispadne,

589
00:34:58,840 --> 00:34:59,800
[SPEAKER_00] to ne podržavam.

590
00:34:59,800 --> 00:35:00,900
[SPEAKER_00] To mi se ne sviđa,

591
00:35:00,900 --> 00:35:02,019
[SPEAKER_00] ali to nisu oni krivi.

592
00:35:02,019 --> 00:35:05,460
[SPEAKER_00] To je jedna kriva interpretacija,

593
00:35:05,460 --> 00:35:08,219
[SPEAKER_00] jedno linčevanje medijsko koje se dogodilo

594
00:35:08,219 --> 00:35:09,760
[SPEAKER_00] bez objektivnog pristupa,

595
00:35:09,760 --> 00:35:11,880
[SPEAKER_00] što to oni žele.

596
00:35:11,880 --> 00:35:14,679
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, neki svećenici su to komentirali,

597
00:35:14,840 --> 00:35:16,880
[SPEAKER_00] tamo davali izjavu koja je bila nespretna.

598
00:35:16,880 --> 00:35:18,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam protiv takve izjave

599
00:35:18,820 --> 00:35:20,119
[SPEAKER_00] koje je dao jedan svećenik tamo.

600
00:35:20,119 --> 00:35:21,500
[SPEAKER_00] Bez da ga osuđujem,

601
00:35:21,500 --> 00:35:24,099
[SPEAKER_00] ali mi se ne sviđa izjava koju je on dao,

602
00:35:24,099 --> 00:35:25,820
[SPEAKER_00] koji su medije onda još ukrenuli,

603
00:35:25,820 --> 00:35:27,019
[SPEAKER_00] izleupotrijebili.

604
00:35:27,019 --> 00:35:28,679
[SPEAKER_00] Pa su snimili još neke čudne ljude

605
00:35:28,679 --> 00:35:30,239
[SPEAKER_00] koji možda njih nisu dio toga

606
00:35:30,239 --> 00:35:33,059
[SPEAKER_00] i njihove izjave putili.

607
00:35:33,059 --> 00:35:34,719
[SPEAKER_00] To je vrlo perfidno napravljeno

608
00:35:34,719 --> 00:35:36,099
[SPEAKER_00] i to nije objektivna slika

609
00:35:36,099 --> 00:35:37,739
[SPEAKER_00] što ta inicijativa je.

610
00:35:37,739 --> 00:35:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ja poznajem tu neke ljude

611
00:35:39,500 --> 00:35:40,719
[SPEAKER_00] i znam da je inicijativa

612
00:35:40,719 --> 00:35:43,519
[SPEAKER_00] dobro smišljenja,

613
00:35:43,519 --> 00:35:45,340
[SPEAKER_00] nadaknuti o duhovom svetim,

614
00:35:45,340 --> 00:35:47,300
[SPEAKER_00] nikoga ne uznemirava.

615
00:35:47,300 --> 00:35:49,280
[SPEAKER_00] Pa to je termin jutarnji,

616
00:35:49,280 --> 00:35:50,980
[SPEAKER_00] subota, ujutro ljudi spavaju.

617
00:35:50,980 --> 00:35:53,139
[SPEAKER_00] Da su htjeli senzaciju,

618
00:35:53,139 --> 00:35:54,559
[SPEAKER_00] bili bi u podnevnom terminu,

619
00:35:54,559 --> 00:35:55,699
[SPEAKER_00] ono kad je špica tamo

620
00:35:55,699 --> 00:35:57,500
[SPEAKER_00] za te kave i tako dalje.

621
00:35:57,500 --> 00:35:59,500
[SPEAKER_00] Oni idu u pola devetu jutro,

622
00:35:59,500 --> 00:36:01,059
[SPEAKER_00] pa kome tad mogu smetati?

623
00:36:01,059 --> 00:36:02,719
[SPEAKER_00] I mole dostajanstvenu, lijepu.

624
00:36:03,780 --> 00:36:05,380
[SPEAKER_00] A očito to uznemirava duhove.

625
00:36:05,380 --> 00:36:06,320
[SPEAKER_00] Krunica je moćna.

626
00:36:06,320 --> 00:36:08,380
[SPEAKER_00] Zato se duhovi uznemiravaju.

627
00:36:08,380 --> 00:36:10,900
[SPEAKER_00] A u isto vrijeme kad neko tamo

628
00:36:10,900 --> 00:36:12,780
[SPEAKER_00] baš u toj špici je uko podneva,

629
00:36:12,780 --> 00:36:14,559
[SPEAKER_00] oni hari krišneka tamo lupaju,

630
00:36:14,559 --> 00:36:16,400
[SPEAKER_00] nikom to ne smeta.

631
00:36:16,400 --> 00:36:19,539
[SPEAKER_00] Sada pa na zapadu

632
00:36:19,539 --> 00:36:21,400
[SPEAKER_00] traže šariatski zakon,

633
00:36:21,400 --> 00:36:22,559
[SPEAKER_00] ispune cijeli trg.

634
00:36:22,559 --> 00:36:24,360
[SPEAKER_00] Radikalni ovi islamisti.

635
00:36:24,360 --> 00:36:27,340
[SPEAKER_00] To isto nema medijske osude od toga.

636
00:36:27,340 --> 00:36:28,619
[SPEAKER_00] To je sve prečudno.

637
00:36:28,619 --> 00:36:29,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje moli njih, ne znam,

638
00:36:29,739 --> 00:36:31,320
[SPEAKER_00] puno manja grupa moli Krunicu

639
00:36:31,320 --> 00:36:32,980
[SPEAKER_00] u terminu kad nema nikoga u gradu,

640
00:36:33,079 --> 00:36:34,880
[SPEAKER_00] praktički i to nekome smeta.

641
00:36:34,880 --> 00:36:36,280
[SPEAKER_00] Božda se zapitamo stvarno.

642
00:36:36,280 --> 00:36:38,019
[SPEAKER_00] Prečudno, evo.

643
00:36:38,019 --> 00:36:38,800
[SPEAKER_01] Jako, da.

644
00:36:38,800 --> 00:36:40,420
[SPEAKER_01] Slažem se s tom pogotovo

645
00:36:40,420 --> 00:36:41,340
[SPEAKER_01] da je to njihovo pravo.

646
00:36:41,340 --> 00:36:42,679
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to je građansko pravo,

647
00:36:42,679 --> 00:36:45,280
[SPEAKER_01] prema tome tu nema što oko toga.

648
00:36:45,280 --> 00:36:48,619
[SPEAKER_01] Jednu našu gledateljicu zanima

649
00:36:48,619 --> 00:36:50,300
[SPEAKER_01] do koje mjere bi mladi

650
00:36:50,300 --> 00:36:53,360
[SPEAKER_01] trebali biti upućeni

651
00:36:53,360 --> 00:36:55,119
[SPEAKER_01] u proučavanje teologije

652
00:36:55,119 --> 00:36:57,480
[SPEAKER_01] i koji je najbolji način

653
00:36:57,480 --> 00:36:59,360
[SPEAKER_01] da mladi laik nauči što više

654
00:36:59,360 --> 00:37:01,360
[SPEAKER_01] o katoličkoj vjeri?

655
00:37:02,380 --> 00:37:06,679
[SPEAKER_01] Do koje bi mjere mladi

656
00:37:06,679 --> 00:37:08,679
[SPEAKER_01] trebali biti upućeni

657
00:37:08,679 --> 00:37:09,920
[SPEAKER_01] u proučavanje teologije

658
00:37:09,920 --> 00:37:11,880
[SPEAKER_01] i koji je najbolji način

659
00:37:11,880 --> 00:37:13,880
[SPEAKER_01] da mladi laik nauči više o vjeri?

660
00:37:16,179 --> 00:37:18,260
[SPEAKER_00] Doroteologija u doslovnom smislu

661
00:37:18,260 --> 00:37:20,360
[SPEAKER_00] svako može upisati, studirati teologiju,

662
00:37:20,360 --> 00:37:21,099
[SPEAKER_00] ali nije nužno.

663
00:37:21,099 --> 00:37:24,480
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, može se rasti

664
00:37:24,480 --> 00:37:25,420
[SPEAKER_00] u teološkoj spoznanja

665
00:37:25,420 --> 00:37:27,019
[SPEAKER_00] i u svojoj svakodnevnici.

666
00:37:27,019 --> 00:37:28,480
[SPEAKER_00] Čitati duhovnu literaturu,

667
00:37:28,480 --> 00:37:29,920
[SPEAKER_00] katekizam katoličke crkve,

668
00:37:29,920 --> 00:37:32,780
[SPEAKER_00] mnoga spisa o svecima

